re":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-20T13:24:25.000Z","msg":"俾著其他國家，一定閂門仲充公埋個公園做主題洒店"},{"pid":"b8122480ed6b07a991d493669099c9a2793fe6e8","tid":566760,"uid":34409,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-20T13:33:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://holland.pk/o9jc85m2\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fo9jc85m2&h=c0be9b65&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n日本迪迪尼年票減價 都有錢賺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0e184c271a5401224c06b70eb8ab6dc4de930f5","tid":566760,"uid":124585,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4de4af627f9689fc9473e72935cb484af95ed220","tid":566760,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-20T08:26:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180220/large/1519113278_3415.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180220%2Flarge%2F1519113278_3415.jpg&h=e3fa62b9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n香港迪士尼樂園連續第3年出現虧損。樂園公佈2017年度業績，去年雖然入場人數及消費額上升，但因場內設施、擴建和營運開支影響，淨虧損由2016年度的1.71億元，擴大至3.45億元，增幅超過一倍。<br />\n<br />\n樂園去年錄得總入場人次有620萬，按年增加10萬人次，其中41%為本地遊客，內地客和國際客則分別佔34%和25%，其中國際客數字創新高，酒店入住率則由2016年近80%下跌至近70%。樂園又指，入園遊客的人均消費錄得4%增幅，是連續第8年創新高，推高收入至51億港元，是開業以來的第二高記錄。稅息折舊及攤銷前利潤則有9.14億元，增幅達28%，是5年以來的新高。不過，若扣除有關款項，樂園實質卻轉盈為虧，倒蝕3.45億元。<br />\n<br />\n雖然連年錄得虧損，但樂園稱仍對市場前景有信心，今年內會推出多個新項目，包括3月先後推出全新8分鐘的「We Love Mickey!」投影盛演及「加利布尼市集」；首個擴建項目舞台表現「魔海奇緣凱旋慶典」將於5月起上演；6月則有以彼思動畫為主題的全新夏日活動「大街水花派對」登場。<br />\n<br />\n翻查資料，迪士尼自2010年有公佈盈虧資料以來，僅得2013年和2014年曾錄有1.09億元和2.42億元的純利，其餘各年派成績表都「見紅」。港府過去多年一直向樂園「泵水」，2016年就曾經再注資58億元，累積「泵水」多達324億元，不過巨額投資卻從未為港府帶來一分一毫的分紅，反被美國迪士尼向港府索取超過2.5億元的專利權及管理費。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180220/57853485\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180220%2F57853485&d=O5GDw088ZA10p07MbgUQib%2BnoHux5cIPnxEj5ZZbdh4%3D&h=a7477344\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180220%2F57853485&h=352a6bce\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180220/57853485</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-20T13:46:55.000Z","msg":"有中國遊客支持, 駛咩驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"26a8dde0da87c6ed76f811524d7b53e9ca815565","tid":566760,"uid":32665,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-20T13:53:48.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"> 唔係政府有份既咩？</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"342a4fd0327cadf0ac8b6b610dee98d9698c96dd","tid":566760,"uid":10637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1537d9fba5eba6873406100f4b7c1ad69be35864","tid":566760,"uid":33059,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-20T10:55:05.000Z","msg":"咁多間迪士尼，<br />\n總有幾間蝕，<br />\n有咩所謂"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-20T13:54:41.000Z","msg":"以前唔係地震帶既迪士尼全部蝕<br />\n我記得巴黎果個蝕得好勁"},{"pid":"966fc116fd6e747de2a634e8d2e8cd4d20ce2a7c","tid":566760,"uid":52358,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-20T14:16:58.000Z","msg":"蝕到nigga奇俠變賣烏干達都救唔返<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34aa23872555b0a2934204e31cd87599989196cf","tid":566760,"uid":42536,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"a11258640b47765e18a1172a9a0bf2973c0b2742","tid":566760,"uid":19275,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-20T11:15:50.000Z","msg":"同高鐵比 真係濕濕碎 <br />\n香港人蝕幾億就咁大反應<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 遲下點熬"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-20T14:21:27.000Z","msg":"又冇講錯，膠鐵港豬噢橋forecast仲蝕得金<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n迪士尼話晒都仲算係屬於香港同香港人，蝕嘅錢當係好似俾旅發局每年宣傳香港嘅費用都好過d直頭賣港送錢嘅大白象"},{"pid":"376c91da343d9bac5a13fdcae57cc8faf974f2c0","tid":566760,"uid":159