oji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n稅息折舊及攤銷前利潤咪即係易必打<br />\n攤銷只係財技 <br />\n做到迪士尼自己條數蝕錢<br />\n之後先可以收貴D你班香港撚屌<br />\n唔係有實錢袋落袋"},{"pid":"e0c1321ca24f7634da961d59a7d127fc1abf4788","tid":566760,"uid":44486,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-20T15:52:15.000Z","msg":"帳面咪蝕<br />\n但一定好似國際學校咁 pump晒水比母公司<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ddaf45d5ab91ed8fa05f88cdf04a8d6ed08d2a38","tid":566760,"uid":146621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-20T16:03:47.000Z","msg":"一次都冇去過<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}